snippet.title: LUIGI'S QUEST: TROUBLE IN SARASALAND - Release Trailer (SMBX2)
snippet.description:
(Shout-out to @Superstarshi  for making this trailer!)

DISCLAIMER: Some of the footage in this trailer is not final, as they've been changed since the creation of the trailer.

Here's the release trailer of Luigi's Quest: Trouble in Sarasaland, the current SMBX2 project of mine in works, themed around Super Mario Land! After a year of development, the episode's finished and ready!

Here's the link to the episode:

https://www.smbxgame.com/forums/viewtopic.php?t=29421

Join my server if you wanna talk about the episode or post your gameplay of it:

https://discord.gg/5mK9Nxgqzm

#smbx #luigi #fangame
